{"tid":1756292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"迫你身邊未登記選民既人做選民","createTime":"2019-11-26T03:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T04:02:21.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2674ae3beae37ee4e4df2122ab695e9597bdf832","tid":1756292,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"迫你身邊未登記選民既人做選民<br />\n<br />\n減去未夠18歲<br />\n睇番數字，有接近二百萬人其實未登記<br />\n每個年齡階層未登記都不同，但18-20只有5成，其他年齡層介乎七十幾-88%，年齡大既登記率好高<br />\n估計這類人是政治唔關我事/唔好煩到我/我手停口停無咁得閒類別人仕<br />\n另外有近3成既人登記左但無投，接受60萬人<br />\n所以其實潛在票源仲有260萬，個數目好多<br />\n但無可否認，呢二百六十萬，好難令佢地轉化成真正票源"},{"pid":"49e7bec14ff9b0a2d563e314b9bd56b00e2143f6","tid":1756292,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線勿鬆懈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV07JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=20052ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"11676eddb400cf7645becfddfa76ee4609c8f3b4","tid":1756292,"uid":160795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"講起捐錢，你會捐去邊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756272</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d92c12a99988dce1a6886acefeafe27d4d87224f","tid":1756292,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"要設死線！今次民意政府冇得唔承認唔回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG